[Pete] Remember the night
when you first confided

79
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:30,674
[Elliott Humming]

80
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:34,429
And things went so right
that we both decided

81
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:38,633
[Elliott Humming]

82
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:42,389
Now we're together
and life is perfect

83
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:45,956
Don't ever disappear

84
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,799
- [Humming]
- Oh, really?

85
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,797
- [Humming]
- Oh, you're just saying that.

86
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:53,718
- [Humming]
- Is it true?

87
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:58,709
- [Humming]
- I love you too

88
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:05,558
We're walking down
a road of our own

89
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:09,229
