[Giggling]

90
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:13,069
I'm glad I don't
have to be alone

91
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:17,876
[Humming, Snorting]

92
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:23,399
You know what to say
when I want direction

93
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:27,399
[Elliott Humming]

94
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:31,274
You don't turn away
when I need protection

95
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,197
[Roaring]

96
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:35,151
[Sneezing]

97
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:38,716
Your voice is the sound
of an angel singing

98
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:42,799
Music I wait to hear

99
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:45,195
- [Humming, Crooning]
- Say it again!

100
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,959
- [Humming, Crooning]
- And again!

101
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:50,071
- [Crooning Continues]
- Everything seems so new!

102
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,839
[Crooning]

103
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:56,953
- I love you too
- [Crooning]

104
00:10:57,080 --> 00:11:00,470
- I love you too
